data.description:
Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the prestigious Avenir community of Palm Beach Gardens. This customized Torrance model home offers a harmonious blend of elegance, sophistication, and modern comforts, providing an unparalleled living experience.

This 5 bedroom 3 bath home is a customized model with impeccable high end finish selections!   Step inside the grand foyer, and you'll immediately be greeted by a sense of spaciousness and refinement. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating a perfect flow for both entertaining and everyday living.

The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream come true, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, a large center island, and breakfast bar seating. The kitchen overlooks the expansive family room, where you can relax in multiple living areas and enjoy  fabulous views of the surrounding beauty through the oversized windows.

The first floor encompasses a formal dining room, a private study/home office, and a guest suite with an en-suite bathroom, providing utmost convenience and flexibility. Upstairs, you'll find the luxurious primary suite, boasting a spacious layout, an oversized laundry room, and a lavish spa-like bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a walk-in shower.


Outside, the expansive backyard oasis beckons you to unwind and enjoy the Florida sunshine. Host gatherings on the oversized covered patio, or savor quiet moments in the beautifully landscaped yard.

This home also includes access to the incredible amenities offered by the Avenir community. From picturesque walking trails to recreational parks, lakes, and the most beautiful clubhouse with tennis, pickleball, fitness center, splash pad, and so much more.  Avenir provides an exceptional lifestyle for residents of all ages.
Located in Palm Beach Gardens, this property offers convenient access to top-rated schools, gourmet dining, world-class shopping, championship golf courses, and pristine beaches. With its unmatched combination of elegance, functionality, and a prime location, 12561 Nautilus Circle is the epitome of luxury living in Avenir and awaits its discerning new owners. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary residence your own.  Welcome to paradise!
